"""
        Tests use of built in DRF filtering with ObjectMultipleModelAPIView
        """
view = SearchFilterView.as_view()
request = factory.get('/', {'search': 'as'})
with self.assertNumQueries(2):
    response = view(request).render()
self.assertEqual(response.status_code, status.HTTP_200_OK)
self.assertEqual(response.data, {'Play': [{'title': 'As You Like It',
    'genre': 'Comedy', 'year': 1623}], 'Poem': [{'title':
    'As a decrepit father takes delight', 'style': 'Sonnet'}]})
